  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose your ship, battle hordes of enemies, and evolve until you meet the BOSS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/4ecbd51c405038ce79fda027fc5ae963.poster.avif?t=1729938439\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/4ecbd51c405038ce79fda027fc5ae963.webm?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/4ecbd51c405038ce79fda027fc5ae963.mp4?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each ship plays differently!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some have automatic weapons that target the nearest enemy, while others are faster, more agile, or more resilient.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can upgrade many features to survive and avoid being overwhelmed by your enemies:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number and power of different weapons, firing rate, accuracy, your speed, your armor...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's up to you to carefully choose what you need to keep fighting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/fd98cf0cd259151e9fd5d62c2a907e6e.poster.avif?t=1729938439\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/fd98cf0cd259151e9fd5d62c2a907e6e.webm?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/fd98cf0cd259151e9fd5d62c2a907e6e.mp4?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Learn to manage your enemies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will encounter formidable enemies throughout your games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set your priorities and adapt: find out how to effectively deal with each of them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to defeat them and adapt to survive their numbers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/31264b8ee32fd620bf2068b06a8eaeec.poster.avif?t=1729938439\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/31264b8ee32fd620bf2068b06a8eaeec.webm?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/31264b8ee32fd620bf2068b06a8eaeec.mp4?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basic Tips</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look for the yellow tiles! They will give you invaluable bonuses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget, XP is the key to your evolution, your survival, and your victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't hesitate to retreat, your priority is to survive until the next wave!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose your ship, battle hordes of enemies, and evolve until you meet the BOSS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/4ecbd51c405038ce79fda027fc5ae963.poster.avif?t=1729938439\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/4ecbd51c405038ce79fda027fc5ae963.webm?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/4ecbd51c405038ce79fda027fc5ae963.mp4?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each ship plays differently!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some have automatic weapons that target the nearest enemy, while others are faster, more agile, or more resilient.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can upgrade many features to survive and avoid being overwhelmed by your enemies:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number and power of different weapons, firing rate, accuracy, your speed, your armor...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's up to you to carefully choose what you need to keep fighting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/fd98cf0cd259151e9fd5d62c2a907e6e.poster.avif?t=1729938439\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/fd98cf0cd259151e9fd5d62c2a907e6e.webm?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/fd98cf0cd259151e9fd5d62c2a907e6e.mp4?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Learn to manage your enemies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will encounter formidable enemies throughout your games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set your priorities and adapt: find out how to effectively deal with each of them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to defeat them and adapt to survive their numbers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/31264b8ee32fd620bf2068b06a8eaeec.poster.avif?t=1729938439\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/31264b8ee32fd620bf2068b06a8eaeec.webm?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239570/extras/31264b8ee32fd620bf2068b06a8eaeec.mp4?t=1729938439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basic Tips</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look for the yellow tiles! They will give you invaluable bonuses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget, XP is the key to your evolution, your survival, and your victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't hesitate to retreat, your priority is to survive until the next wave!</p>",
